itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/whofkcare221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwhofkcare221&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1411e071\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/whofkcare221</a>"},{"pid":"48f90c982c4c292474f2165c8cc04f56740bb1f3","tid":907521,"uid":20115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T18:02:49.000Z","msg":"人總是盲目，為了追求自己所喜，而無視了、放棄了身旁的人。長久以來的相識到最後換來一生的悲傷，如果可以選擇，我相信人寧願選擇後悔，可是人就是犯賤，經過一次、二次、三次的傷害還追尋朋友、情人。<br />\n<br />\n沒有什麼事比孤單可怕，在社會人是群體的動物，但人是一種求利的、會為所喜放棄一直為自己付出的人，即使朋友還是情人，只要遇上新合適人選便會把原有的掉去"},{"pid":"291d9e20ca780bb3ba74bb81bdd9b2c05bc2ae5f","tid":907521,"uid":27745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T18:12:08.000Z","msg":"真係好勸世<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我5年幾了 仲勁過毒癮 點甩"},{"pid":"907847eb20e525b0449c047d41b23240b540a29f","tid":907521,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"